title: Thom Hartmann Program - September 25 2013
description:
September 25, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: Who is turning U.S. students against their own nation?  Frank Vernuccio, NY Analysis of Policy & Government / Plus, how do we eliminate global poverty by 2030?  Michael Elliot, ONE Campaign

Hour Two: The Pope speaks out about capitalism - William Donohue, Catholic League for Religious and Civil Rights

Hour Three: Global warming to claim half a billion people...
